Unity Master Server

1.0.0 (04/03/08)

- Added command line parameters for setting the most used options, (use -? to see them).
- Added signal handler for Ctrl-C so it exits cleanly.
- Fixed some compile errors when using Visual Studio 2003 on Windows
- Bugfixes for long term stability
- Added option to print statistics at specific intervals (nr. of queries/active games etc).
- Added option to print to log file instead of stdout, file is rotate when 50MB is reached.

0.1.0 (10/10/07)

- Initial version
